---
/**
 * Redesigned Conclusion Section (Ready to restore)
 */
---

<section class="ready section-pad reveal">
    <div class="container text-center">
        <h2>Ready to restore?</h2>
        <p>
            A simple, natural way to dissolve stress at its source and restore
            your true nature.
        </p>
        <div style="margin-top: 48px;">
            <a href="#book" class="btn btn--primary" style="min-width: 240px;"
                >Book a Session</a
            >
        </div>

        <div class="ready-footer reveal">
            <p>
                Meditation that is personal, individual, effective and serves
                the greater common good.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .ready {
        background: var(--color-warm-white);
    }
    .ready h2 {
        font-size: clamp(32px, 5vw, 56px);
        font-style: italic;
        color: var(--color-indigo);
        margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .ready p {
        font-size: clamp(17px, 2vw, 20px);
        color: var(--color-slate);
        max-width: 580px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        line-height: 1.8;
    }
    .ready-footer {
        margin-top: 80px;
        padding-top: 40px;
        border-top: 1px solid var(--color-mist);
    }
    .ready-footer p {
        font-size: 14px;
        letter-spacing: 1px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: var(--color-eucalyptus);
        max-width: 100%;
    }
</style>
